description: After 48 years, evangelical pastor Dr. Tony Evans is calling it quits at his church because of an unknown sin he committed. The popular pastor was once the chaplain for the Dallas Cowboys and Mavericks.
title: Evangelical Texas pastor reveals he's quitting because of mysterious 'sin' he committed in the past

description: Surveillance footage from Ypsilanti Middle School shows a coach stalking Michael Moon, 14, as he walked down a hallway last week and strangling him with a shirt.
title: Middle school coach caught on video sneaking up behind and choking 14-year-old with shirt

description: An environmental group dedicated to protecting the endangered Pacific pocket mouse is appealing to Dana Point's Planning Commission decision to restrict daily public use of a trail at Dana Point.
title: Wealthy hikers go to war with environmental activists trying to BAN them from popular viewpoint over threat to endangered wildlife

description: Locals living near the Wolverhampton park where the 19-year-old was butchered to death in a brutal killing told of how one of the tearaways was a 'nasty piece of work'.
title: Neighbour of boy, 12, who murdered Shawn Seesahai, 19, with a 16-inch machete reveals he had to put up barbed wire to keep him off his property and calls him 'twisted in the head'

description: The Ross Lake House hotel in Rosscahill, owned by Americans Allan Stringer and his wife Shannon Kincaid, was set alight on December 16, just hours after an anti-migrant protest at the site.
title: I lost my mother's ashes in hotel fire started by suspected anti-migrant arsonists in Ireland, says heartbroken owner of Galway's Lake House - which once hosted Hollywood icon Maureen O'Hara

description: Just 24 per cent of people now agree that trans people should be allowed to change their sex 'if they want' - compared to support levels of 58 per cent in 2016.
title: Public support for transgender people's ability to change sex on their birth certificate collapses compared to recent years, major study reveals

description: Unlike you-know-who, Joe Biden did not duck out of his D-Day duties last Thursday. But was he really all there? The videos suggest that he was not.
title: Sadly, it's now impossible to deny that Joe Biden, the most powerful man in the world, is increasingly loopy - and getting worse, writes FREDDY GRAY

description: Labour was mocked yesterday over a 'dodgy dossier' claiming the Tories' pledges would send annual mortgage payments soaring by £4,800.
title: Rachel Reeves ridiculed for publishing 'dodgy dossier' - that claimed Tory tax cuts were 'unfunded' - twice after 'embarrassing' document had pluses and minuses mixed up

description: Malahki Gray, 25, was found dead at the quarry near Mt Ngungun, north of Brisbane, on Tuesday, bringing to end a two-week search.
title: Body is found dumped at an abandoned quarry as grim search for missing son ends and two men are charged

description: Research has shown that Chatsworth House in the picturesque Derbyshire Dales is the most popular real-life television and movie location in Britain.
title: The Darcy effect: Chatsworth House where Pride and Prejudice was filmed is the most popular real-life television and movie location in Britain

description: Wes Steeting sparked fears that Labour could increase the duty on the sale of assets in its first budget to raise money.
title: Fears mount over potential Labour gains tax hike as Wes Streeting refuses to rule out changes to duty on sale of assets - despite being asked four times

description: According to Italian news agency ANSA, Pope Francis , 87, repeated the term on Tuesday as he met Roman priests, saying 'there is an air of f*****ness in the Vatican'.
title: Pope Francis 'repeats gay slur' just weeks after being forced to apologise for saying there was 'an air of f*****ry' in the church

description: Some Australians have lost their life savings in an alleged tiny homes scam which has left around 170 creditors owed an estimated $6million.
title: How buying a tiny home turned into a nightmare for this Aussie couple: 'It makes me feel sick'
